{"tid":2332822,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"成日生眼瘡  眼皮又重又腫","createTime":"2020-12-20T02:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T05:38:36.000Z","uid":94970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5123f3d64b7b69277f2afa52c76b0b58789b9654","tid":2332822,"uid":94970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:26:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人成日生眼瘡 但細細粒 未去到要做手術割<br />\n<br />\n用熱敷好返後  眼皮都keep住又重又腫 起碼持續幾個星期<br />\n<br />\n聽日講會搞到眼瞼下垂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人有類似經驗"},{"pid":"ab88c5995eff83d5c3ba05abf7175913ef988053","tid":2332822,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:32:52.000Z","msg":"My name"},{"pid":"4c221041809e682d017d66a08f6f3818f7e34464","tid":2332822,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:40:57.000Z","msg":"睇醫生 拎眼膏啦 幾日就消腫啦"},{"pid":"be45dbaac6c5684e3f444183c71c07cad1a72a6c","tid":2332822,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"有無人有眼科醫生介紹，唔好咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近排少左收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5596d464ff6d780e8675e3d0e59d97f2adf3bec","tid":2332822,"uid":94970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c221041809e682d017d66a08f6f3818f7e34464","tid":2332822,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:40:57.000Z","msg":"睇醫生 拎眼膏啦 幾日就消腫啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:49:13.000Z","msg":"有冇醫生介紹 睇普通門診個啲都消唔到腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93174fa7638b0c78a4cd48e2191f7d975eed3d3","tid":2332822,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5596d464ff6d780e8675e3d0e59d97f2adf3bec","tid":2332822,"uid":94970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c221041809e682d017d66a08f6f3818f7e34464","tid":2332822,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:40:57.000Z","msg":"睇醫生 拎眼膏啦 幾日就消腫啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:49:13.000Z","msg":"有冇醫生介紹 睇普通門診個啲都消唔到腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:50:56.000Z","msg":"臨瞓射落隻眼嗰隻喎<br />\n咁都唔得就睇眼科啦"},{"pid":"e5c855cbcbe052a0c5c14e968c93ea827aba1b2a","tid":2332822,"uid":36546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"係咪有污糟既野？... 之前我都係咁，後尾發覺係mouse pad 污糟，掉左就無晒事"},{"pid":"a66fde37795d7c283273ffd4c60aa70094d13d85","tid":2332822,"uid":94970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5c855cbcbe052a0c5c14e968c93ea827aba1b2a","tid":2332822,"uid":36546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"係咪有污糟既野？... 之前我都係咁，後尾發覺係mouse pad 污糟，掉左就無晒事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"所以你捽眼搞到咁？"},{"pid":"f2af96c3db474019363a49e3a745acd1912d93c5","tid":2332822,"uid":123752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:31:42.000Z","msg":"通常我隻眼紅/腫都係因為落妝/搽護膚品果陣唔小心入眼<br />\n每隔一段時間,右眼既下眼瞼入面就會生眼瘡<br />\n等佢熟左再擠粒白色酒米出黎好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW早排左眼急性結膜炎,病發前一晚臨訓前隻眼突然好痛紅晒<br />\n跟住唔理佢照訓教,第二朝醒左腫到仆街<br />\n落樓下診所睇醫生,醫生開左眼藥水<br />\n滴左3-4日左右就好返"},{"pid":"c13972047597019af5d0294f8587830a55781d7a","tid":2332822,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"唔好用手 毛巾 污糟水掂到隻眼<br />\n清水洗臉由佢自然乾"},{"pid":"597b2a036271e97d5ebd36eff29ee6a65f2e40ed","tid":2332822,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"家庭醫生開左藥，無效，佢叫我食完藥無用就去睇專科，唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6d87c2dd8b2290928a7fb5686c5a775e090a5b","tid":2332822,"uid":49363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:27:21.000Z","msg":"去盲人輔導會睇可以切眼瘡<br />\n或攞轉介去政府排眼科"},{"pid":"1db7a5345729c661b8372ff6db6fa7b4ad1089c9","tid":2332822,"uid":258529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:35:06.000Z","msg":"之前都成日生腫到比人打咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲會成日都有一粒粒黃白色好似粉刺咁係眼瞼到但唔痛唔痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個醫生同我講平時沖涼開花灑用暖水圍住眼肚個位淋15-20秒<br />\n跟住醫生講晚晚咁做之後就冇生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd3dee6d544bb7bff80e5a4f502fd5debf99f0d","tid":2332822,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a6d87c2dd8b2290928a7fb5686c5a775e090a5b","tid":2332822,"uid":49363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:27:21.000Z","msg":"去盲人輔導會睇可以切眼瘡<br />\n或攞轉介去政府排眼科"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"政府條隊係咪長到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e534b91d57b8002fcfff57bfd43f12fcb1e76b8","tid":2332822,"uid":94970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1db7a5345729c661b8372ff6db6fa7b4ad1089c9","tid":2332822,"uid":258529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:35:06.000Z","msg":"之前都成日生腫到比人打咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲會成日都有一粒粒黃白色好似粉刺咁係眼瞼到但唔痛唔痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個醫生同我講平時沖涼開花灑用暖水圍住眼肚個位淋15-20秒<br />\n跟住醫生講晚晚咁做之後就冇生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T00:56:02.000Z","msg":"眼肚?<br />\n<br />\n但我係上眼皮生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896db4ce951e9c77d740367d663b3e96b9d9fac7","tid":2332822,"uid":258529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e534b91d57b8002fcfff57bfd43f12fcb1e76b8","tid":2332822,"uid":94970,"like":0,"d